<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-18-0267 </DOCNO><TEXT>This chapter is intended to serve as a guide to those called upon to negotiateand draft a joint venture agreement in the Eastern coal industry. Jointventure agreements have never been as widely used in the Eastern coalindustry as they have in the West where the larger size of the minesrequires a greater capital investment, and thus makes a sharing of therisk more prudent.</TEXT></DOC>